# Documentation — all .md files excluded from git tracking
# (operator preference: docs are private; design/strategy/phase
# reports live on disk only). One exception: the ROOT README.md
# is the repository's front-page; tracked so it renders on the git
# host. Subdirectory README.md files (apps/*/README.md, docs/, etc.)
# stay private.
*.md
!/README.md
!docs/SCENARIOS.md
!docs/XGENGUARDIAN_INTEGRATION_SPEC.md
!docs/KILL_CHAIN_COVERAGE.md
!docs/REAL_USE_CASES.md

